      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200059,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Technical Implementation\n\nFiles: stop.service.ts, haversine.ts\n       stop.routes.ts\nTables: stops, route_stops\n\nGeocoding strategy (seed time):\n  1. stops_geocoded.csv (exact match)\n  2. osm_bus_stops.json (fuzzy match)\n     Normalized strings, ≥60% similarity\n\nNo PostGIS dependency — pure JS math\nTamil name support: nameTa column",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m3_tech",
      "originalText": "Technical Implementation\n\nFiles: stop.service.ts, haversine.ts\n       stop.routes.ts\nTables: stops, route_stops\n\nGeocoding strategy (seed time):\n  1. stops_geocoded.csv (exact match)\n  2. osm_bus_stops.json (fuzzy match)\n     Normalized strings, ≥60% similarity\n\nNo PostGIS dependency — pure JS math\nTamil name support: nameTa column",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
