    {
      "id": "m4_desc_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 140,
      "y": 1305,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 130,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200068,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200069,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose & Overview\n\nManages the full lifecycle of a\nbus trip from start to completion.\nValidates bus availability, prevents\nconflicts (one active trip per bus),\nregisters in Redis for tracking,\nand cleans up on trip end.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m4_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose & Overview\n\nManages the full lifecycle of a\nbus trip from start to completion.\nValidates bus availability, prevents\nconflicts (one active trip per bus),\nregisters in Redis for tracking,\nand cleans up on trip end.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m4_data",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 750,
      "y": 1240,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 260,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "backgroundColor": "#e7f5ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0z",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 200070,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200071,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "m4_data_t"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "m4_data_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 760,
      "y": 1265,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b10",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200072,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200073,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "State Machine & Data Flow\n\nStates: scheduled → active → completed\n                          → cancelled\n\nSTART: Validate bus not in active trip\n  → INSERT trip (status=active)\n  → SADD route:{id}:trips in Redis\n  → Begin GPS tracking\n\nEND:   UPDATE status=completed\n  → SREM from Redis route set\n  → DEL bus:{tripId} hash\n  → Stop GPS tracking",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m4_data",
      "originalText": "State Machine & Data Flow\n\nStates: scheduled → active → completed\n                          → cancelled\n\nSTART: Validate bus not in active trip\n  → INSERT trip (status=active)\n  → SADD route:{id}:trips in Redis\n  → Begin GPS tracking\n\nEND:   UPDATE status=completed\n  → SREM from Redis route set\n  → DEL bus:{tripId} hash\n  → Stop GPS tracking",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
