      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose & Overview\n\nDual authentication strategy:\n  Drivers: Magic link (passwordless)\n  Admins: Email + password (bcrypt)\n\nJWT-based session management\nwith 7-day token expiry.\nRole-based access control for\nadmin, driver, and conductor.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m5_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose & Overview\n\nDual authentication strategy:\n  Drivers: Magic link (passwordless)\n  Admins: Email + password (bcrypt)\n\nJWT-based session management\nwith 7-day token expiry.\nRole-based access control for\nadmin, driver, and conductor.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
