    {
      "id": "m8_desc_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 140,
      "y": 2647.5,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 195,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200136,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200137,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose & Overview\n\nUnified data access through Drizzle ORM with Effect-based\nerror handling. All database operations return Effect monads\nthat are unwrapped by the Effect handler middleware.\n\nError Mapping:\n  NotFoundError     → 404    AuthError      → 401\n  ForbiddenError    → 403    ConflictError  → 409\n  ValidationError   → 400    UnknownError   → 500\n\nResponse format: { success: boolean, data?, error? }",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m8_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose & Overview\n\nUnified data access through Drizzle ORM with Effect-based\nerror handling. All database operations return Effect monads\nthat are unwrapped by the Effect handler middleware.\n\nError Mapping:\n  NotFoundError     → 404    AuthError      → 401\n  ForbiddenError    → 403    ConflictError  → 409\n  ValidationError   → 400    UnknownError   → 500\n\nResponse format: { success: boolean, data?, error? }",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m8_tech",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1130,
      "y": 2620,
      "width": 980,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1x",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 200138,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200139,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "m8_tech_t"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "m8_tech_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1140,
      "y": 2647.5,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 195,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200140,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200141,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Technical Stack\n\nORM:      Drizzle (type-safe, SQL-like API)\nAdapter:  Neon HTTP (serverless PostgreSQL)\nCache:    Redis (ioredis, lazy connect)\nRuntime:  Bun (fast crypto, password hashing)\n\nShared Validation (Zod):\n  @bus/shared schemas used by both server & clients\n  CreateBusSchema, StartTripSchema, NearbyStopsSchema\n  AdminLoginSchema, MagicLinkRequestSchema, etc.\n\nID Generation: CUID2 (collision-resistant, sortable)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m8_tech",
      "originalText": "Technical Stack\n\nORM:      Drizzle (type-safe, SQL-like API)\nAdapter:  Neon HTTP (serverless PostgreSQL)\nCache:    Redis (ioredis, lazy connect)\nRuntime:  Bun (fast crypto, password hashing)\n\nShared Validation (Zod):\n  @bus/shared schemas used by both server & clients\n  CreateBusSchema, StartTripSchema, NearbyStopsSchema\n  AdminLoginSchema, MagicLinkRequestSchema, etc.\n\nID Generation: CUID2 (collision-resistant, sortable)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
