    {
      "id": "m9_desc_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 140,
      "y": 3005.625,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 178.75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b23",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200150,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200151,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose & Overview\n\nEnables continuous GPS tracking for drivers even when the\napp is in the background. Uses expo-task-manager to define\na persistent background task with a foreground notification.\n\nConfiguration:\n  Interval:  10 seconds between updates\n  Distance:  10 meters minimum movement threshold\n  Accuracy:  BestForNavigation (highest GPS accuracy)\n  Notification: \"Bus Tracker: Tracking your location\"",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "m9_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose & Overview\n\nEnables continuous GPS tracking for drivers even when the\napp is in the background. Uses expo-task-manager to define\na persistent background task with a foreground notification.\n\nConfiguration:\n  Interval:  10 seconds between updates\n  Distance:  10 meters minimum movement threshold\n  Accuracy:  BestForNavigation (highest GPS accuracy)\n  Notification: \"Bus Tracker: Tracking your location\"",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "m9_tech",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1130,
      "y": 2970,
      "width": 980,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
