      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew files:\n  eta.service.ts — calculation logic\n  eta.routes.ts — GET /eta/:tripId/:stopId\n\nNew table: stop_travel_times\n  routeId, fromStopSeq, toStopSeq,\n  avgDuration, sampleCount,\n  timeOfDay (morning/noon/evening/night)\n\nSocket event: eta:update → passengers\nIntegration: trip_locations historical data\nCache: Redis hash eta:{tripId}:{stopId}",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f1_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew files:\n  eta.service.ts — calculation logic\n  eta.routes.ts — GET /eta/:tripId/:stopId\n\nNew table: stop_travel_times\n  routeId, fromStopSeq, toStopSeq,\n  avgDuration, sampleCount,\n  timeOfDay (morning/noon/evening/night)\n\nSocket event: eta:update → passengers\nIntegration: trip_locations historical data\nCache: Redis hash eta:{tripId}:{stopId}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
