    {
      "id": "f2_impl_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5310,
      "y": 605,
      "width": 1290,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200192,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200193,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nTechnology: expo-notifications (mobile) + Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)\n            Web Push API + Service Worker (web admin)\n\nNew table: notification_subscriptions\n  userId, routeId?, stopId?, type (approaching/started/alert)\n  deviceToken, platform (ios/android/web), enabled\n\nNew service: notification.service.ts\n  subscribe(userId, config) · unsubscribe(id)\n  send(userId, payload) · broadcastRoute(routeId, payload)\n\nTrigger: Hook into tracking.service.ts → check subscriptions on bus:moved",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f2_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nTechnology: expo-notifications (mobile) + Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM)\n            Web Push API + Service Worker (web admin)\n\nNew table: notification_subscriptions\n  userId, routeId?, stopId?, type (approaching/started/alert)\n  deviceToken, platform (ios/android/web), enabled\n\nNew service: notification.service.ts\n  subscribe(userId, config) · unsubscribe(id)\n  send(userId, payload) · broadcastRoute(routeId, payload)\n\nTrigger: Hook into tracking.service.ts → check subscriptions on bus:moved",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
