      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew tables:\n  fare_rules: routeId, busType, baseFare, perKmRate, minFare, maxFare\n  fare_zones: zoneId, name, stops[]\n  concessions: type (student/senior/pass), discountPercent\n\nNew service: fare.service.ts\n  calculate(routeId, fromStopSeq, toStopSeq, busType, concession?)\n  → { fare, distance, stops, breakdown }\n\nAPI: GET /fare?route=R1&from=5&to=15&type=regular\nMobile: Fare calculator screen with stop picker",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f4_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew tables:\n  fare_rules: routeId, busType, baseFare, perKmRate, minFare, maxFare\n  fare_zones: zoneId, name, stops[]\n  concessions: type (student/senior/pass), discountPercent\n\nNew service: fare.service.ts\n  calculate(routeId, fromStopSeq, toStopSeq, busType, concession?)\n  → { fare, distance, stops, breakdown }\n\nAPI: GET /fare?route=R1&from=5&to=15&type=regular\nMobile: Fare calculator screen with stop picker",
