    {
      "id": "f5_desc_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4640,
      "y": 1654.375,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 211.25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b37",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200230,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200231,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose\n\nDefine and manage bus timetables\nwith scheduled departure times.\nTrack adherence (on-time/late/early)\nand show upcoming departures to\npassengers.\n\nFeatures:\n  Daily schedule templates\n  Weekday vs weekend schedules\n  Holiday overrides\n  Punctuality tracking",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f5_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose\n\nDefine and manage bus timetables\nwith scheduled departure times.\nTrack adherence (on-time/late/early)\nand show upcoming departures to\npassengers.\n\nFeatures:\n  Daily schedule templates\n  Weekday vs weekend schedules\n  Holiday overrides\n  Punctuality tracking",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "f5_impl",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 5300,
      "y": 1630,
      "width": 1310,
      "height": 260,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b38",
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3
      },
      "seed": 200232,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200233,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "f5_impl_t"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "f5_impl_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5310,
      "y": 1662.5,
      "width": 1290,
      "height": 195,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b39",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200234,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200235,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew tables:\n  schedules: routeId, busId, driverId, dayType (weekday/weekend/holiday)\n  schedule_times: scheduleId, stopId, departureTime, arrivalTime\n  schedule_overrides: date, scheduleId, status (cancelled/modified)\n\nNew service: schedule.service.ts\n  getUpcoming(stopId, limit) → next N departures from this stop\n  getAdherence(tripId) → { onTime, delay, early } per stop\n\nMobile: \"Next bus\" widget on stop detail page\nAdmin: Schedule builder with drag-and-drop",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f5_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew tables:\n  schedules: routeId, busId, driverId, dayType (weekday/weekend/holiday)\n  schedule_times: scheduleId, stopId, departureTime, arrivalTime\n  schedule_overrides: date, scheduleId, status (cancelled/modified)\n\nNew service: schedule.service.ts\n  getUpcoming(stopId, limit) → next N departures from this stop\n  getAdherence(tripId) → { onTime, delay, early } per stop\n\nMobile: \"Next bus\" widget on stop detail page\nAdmin: Schedule builder with drag-and-drop",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
