      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nAdd to trips table: currentOccupancy, maxCapacity\nNew table: occupancy_reports (crowdsourced)\n  tripId, reportedBy, level, timestamp\n\nSocket event: occupancy:update → broadcast to route trackers\nDriver app: Quick buttons (Empty / Low / Medium / High / Full)\nPassenger app: Color-coded bus markers on map\n  Green (empty) → Yellow → Orange → Red (full)\n\nAdmin dashboard: Occupancy heatmap by route/time",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f6_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nAdd to trips table: currentOccupancy, maxCapacity\nNew table: occupancy_reports (crowdsourced)\n  tripId, reportedBy, level, timestamp\n\nSocket event: occupancy:update → broadcast to route trackers\nDriver app: Quick buttons (Empty / Low / Medium / High / Full)\nPassenger app: Color-coded bus markers on map\n  Green (empty) → Yellow → Orange → Red (full)\n\nAdmin dashboard: Occupancy heatmap by route/time",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
