      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose\n\nCreate virtual geographic boundaries\naround stops, depots, and zones.\nTrigger automated actions when buses\nenter or exit these zones.\n\nUse cases:\n  \"Bus arriving at your stop\" alert\n  Depot entry/exit logging\n  Route deviation detection\n  Speed zone enforcement",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f7_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose\n\nCreate virtual geographic boundaries\naround stops, depots, and zones.\nTrigger automated actions when buses\nenter or exit these zones.\n\nUse cases:\n  \"Bus arriving at your stop\" alert\n  Depot entry/exit logging\n  Route deviation detection\n  Speed zone enforcement",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
