      "text": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew table: geofences\n  id, name, type (circle/polygon), lat, lng, radius,\n  polygon (JSON), action (alert/log/restrict), active\n\nServer: Check geofences on each location:update\n  Redis SET geofence:{busId}:inside for state tracking\n  Emit geofence:enter / geofence:exit events\n\nIntegration: Haversine for circle fences\n             Point-in-polygon for complex zones\nMobile: expo-location geofencing API (native)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f7_impl",
      "originalText": "Implementation Plan\n\nNew table: geofences\n  id, name, type (circle/polygon), lat, lng, radius,\n  polygon (JSON), action (alert/log/restrict), active\n\nServer: Check geofences on each location:update\n  Redis SET geofence:{busId}:inside for state tracking\n  Emit geofence:enter / geofence:exit events\n\nIntegration: Haversine for circle fences\n             Point-in-polygon for complex zones\nMobile: expo-location geofencing API (native)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
