    {
      "id": "f10_desc_t",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4640,
      "y": 3288.75,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 162.5,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b46",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 200300,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 200301,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Purpose\n\nEnable cashless fare payment through\nUPI, digital wallets, and QR-based\nticketing. Generate digital tickets\nwith QR codes for conductor scanning.\n\nMethods: UPI (Razorpay/PhonePe),\n  Digital wallet, Monthly/daily pass,\n  QR ticket",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "f10_desc",
      "originalText": "Purpose\n\nEnable cashless fare payment through\nUPI, digital wallets, and QR-based\nticketing. Generate digital tickets\nwith QR codes for conductor scanning.\n\nMethods: UPI (Razorpay/PhonePe),\n  Digital wallet, Monthly/daily pass,\n  QR ticket",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "f10_impl",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 5300,
      "y": 3260,
      "width": 1310,
      "height": 220,
      "angle": 0,
