      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Implementation Notes\n\nHigh priority modules can be built on top of existing infrastructure (Redis, Socket.IO, trip_locations).\nMedium priority modules need moderate new infrastructure. Future modules require external integrations\n(payment gateways, weather APIs) or significant new features (offline storage, ML models).",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "pri_note",
      "originalText": "Implementation Notes\n\nHigh priority modules can be built on top of existing infrastructure (Redis, Socket.IO, trip_locations).\nMedium priority modules need moderate new infrastructure. Future modules require external integrations\n(payment gateways, weather APIs) or significant new features (offline storage, ML models).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
